lyrics:
[Verse]
I'm hustlin' hard on these streets, tryna stack that cash
But every day feels like an uphill climb, no time to relax
Chasin' dreams of success, but reality bites back
The struggle's real, money's fleeting, it's a never-ending act

[Chorus]
In this game of life, where the struggle's tight
I'm tryna chase that money, gotta grind day and night
But sometimes it feels like I'm caught in a losing fight
I'm just tryna make a future, shining oh so bright
